        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Injunctive Authority Clarification Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits federal courts from issuing injunctive orders that bar enforcement of a federal law or policy against a nonparty, unless the nonparty is represented by a party in a class action lawsuit.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
